description:
Danny recaps the wonderful Real Housewives of New Jersey finale, which ended in Nashville with a lot of sweat and a shocking bedazzled blazer that we need to discuss at length. Danny also BRIEFLY dips into the Selling Sunset empan*das and then the RHOC reunion!
